OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781611874
OL,3,COver 6,000 swimmers attempt the Great
OL,4,CNorth Swim
OL,6,FThe Great North Swim has been held on
OL,7,FWindermere since 2008 and has grown to
OL,8,Fbecome the largest open water swimming
OL,9,Fevent in the UK, regularly attracting
OL,10,Faround 7,500 competitors and 20,000
OL,11,Fspectators.
OL,13,FThis year entries have been a little
OL,14,Flower with 6,500 competitors - and
OL,15,Fmost events have not sold out.
OL,17,FOrganisers say they do a lot in
OL,18,Fresponse to concerns about water
OL,19,Fquality.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781611874
OL,3,COver 6,000 swimmers attempt the Great
OL,4,CNorth Swim
OL,6,FEvent Director Colin Murphy told ITV
OL,7,FBorder: "We have got an upward trend
OL,8,Fthis year on swimming, but also behind
OL,9,Fthe scenes we do rigorous water
OL,10,Ftesting. So we can be confident that
OL,11,Fwe do send people into safe water."
OL,13,FAmong the first swimmers on Friday
OL,14,FJune 12 was Katie Taylor-Rossall from
OL,15,FPreston, raising money in memory of
OL,16,Fher sister Claire, who Katie says died
OL,17,F10 years ago, "really suddenly out on
OL,18,Fa run like any other day, and suddenly
OL,19,Fcollapsed and passed away, with no
OL,20,Fsigns or symptoms that there was
OL,21,Fanything wrong."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781611874
OL,3,COver 6,000 swimmers attempt the Great
OL,4,CNorth Swim
OL,6,FOn the tenth anniversary of her death,
OL,7,FKatie and her family are trying to
OL,8,Fraise #10,000 for the charity Cardiac
OL,9,FRisk in the Young.
OL,11,FKatie added: "Following that massive
OL,12,Ftragedy for our family, Cardiac Risk
OL,13,Fin the Young helped us by testing my
OL,14,Ffamily to make sure that our hearts
OL,15,Fwere okay and that there was nothing
OL,16,Fgoing to happen to us."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781611874
OL,3,COver 6,000 swimmers attempt the Great
OL,4,CNorth Swim
OL,6,FThe Great North Swim is the first of
OL,7,Fthree swimming challenges Katie plans
OL,8,Fto do this year. She is undertaking
OL,9,Fthe five kilometre distance and says,
OL,10,F"I am so far out of my comfort zone.
OL,11,FNervous but excited to give it a go
OL,12,Fand get wet today."
OL,14,FThis year the Lake District Foundation
OL,15,Fwill receive #5 for every swimmer that
OL,16,Fbeats their expected time - up to the
OL,17,Fvalue of #10,000.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781611874
OL,3,COver 6,000 swimmers attempt the Great
OL,4,CNorth Swim
OL,6,FAnya Kuliszewski told ITV Border: "If
OL,7,Fwe do raise #10,000, that's going to
OL,8,Fmake a fantastic difference to
OL,9,Fconservation projects across the Lake
OL,10,FDistrict, including water quality and
OL,11,Fprojects like Fix the Fells and create
OL,12,Fnew reed beds around Windermere."
OL,14,FThe council has warned visitors to the
OL,15,FLake District that the roads are
OL,16,Flikely to be be extremely busy this
OL,17,Fweekend with both the Great North Swim
OL,18,Fand the Windermere Marathon taking
OL,19,Fplace. Organisers say they are trying
OL,20,Fto reduce the impact.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781611874
OL,3,COver 6,000 swimmers attempt the Great
OL,4,CNorth Swim
OL,6,FEvent Director Mr Murphy added: "We
OL,7,Fhave our dedicated park and ride. So
OL,8,Fwe're going to move around 2,000
OL,9,Fpeople on that service over the
OL,10,Fweekend, making sure the roads are
OL,11,Ffree for those who want to enjoy the
OL,12,Flakes for other purposes."
OL,14,FParalympian Lyndon Longhorne is one of
OL,15,Fthe superstars in the water on the
OL,16,Ffirst day of the three-day event. He
OL,17,Fis a quad amputee, so he swims using
OL,18,Fonly his upper body. He told ITV News:
OL,19,F"I've done it for 12 years so I've
OL,20,Fnever had an issue with swimming."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781611874
OL,3,COver 6,000 swimmers attempt the Great
OL,4,CNorth Swim
OL,6,FHe does, however, want to encourage
OL,7,Fanyone with a disability that while it
OL,8,Fmay feel daunting at first, anything
OL,9,Fis possible.
OL,11,FHe said: "For me, getting in the water
OL,12,Fto start with was quite difficult
OL,13,Fbecause you don't know what you can
OL,14,Fdo; what your capabilities are. You
OL,15,Fautomatically start thinking can I
OL,16,Factually do this? But anybody can do
OL,17,Fit."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,326,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1781611874
OL,3,COver 6,000 swimmers attempt the Great
OL,4,CNorth Swim
OL,6,FMr Longhorne, speaking before taking
OL,7,Fon the 10 kilometre swim, continued:
OL,8,F"It's all about your mindset. Yes your
OL,9,Fmind will want to give up first but
OL,10,Fyour body's a lot stronger than you
OL,11,Factually think. If you can adapt to
OL,12,Fany situation, it'll massively open up
OL,13,Fthe doors for more opportunities."
OL,15,FThere were huge cheers when he got
OL,16,Finto the water.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
